title: Iowa poll: Ben Carson leading Donald Trump by 14 points
text:
Published By: USATODAY.com: Washington - Today 
A new poll from Monmouth University shows Ben Carson has pulled away from Donald Trump in a survey of likely Iowa Republican voters.
